    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen ASME V&V 40 credibility factors have been assessed and all meet or exceed the required gradation levels for the declared model risk level. The Use error factor was not assessed on the basis that the simulation workflow is fully automated; the team judged this factor inapplicable. The overall credibility evidence is considered sufficient to support the regulatory submission decision that the CFD model adequately predicts relative hemolysis index for the CPB device across the five target operating conditions.",
